- debian
    build with :
        dpkg-buildpackage -uc -us

    for skipping signing package.


- suse
    build with command in rpmbuild directory: 
    
        rpmbuild -v -ba SPECS/vscripts.spec  
    
    rpmbuild directory has to have the following structure
    
    rpmbuild
    |
    ├── BUILD
    ├── BUILDROOT
    ├── RPMS
    │   └── noarch
    ├── SOURCES
    │   └── vscripts-<version>.tar.gz
    ├── SPECS
    │   └── vscripts.spec
    └── SRPMS
    
- redhat/fedora/centos

    build with command in ~/rpmbuild directory: 
    
        rpmbuild -v -ba SPECS/vscripts.rh.spec  

    rpmbuild
    |
    ├── BUILD
    ├── BUILDROOT
    ├── RPMS
    │   └── noarch
    ├── SOURCES
    │   └── vscripts-<version>.tar.gz
    ├── SPECS
    │   └── vscripts.rh.spec
    └── SRPMS
